<font color="#FF0000">WILD RIDE!</font><br>
<tt>Thu Oct 30 21:23:33 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Talk is cheap..I talk alot..sometimes sane..often silly.  Usually I talk around things..or hit the peaks avoiding the valleys.  But talk is the only tool that I have to dig up the ghosts.  I am inclined to believe that writing is a better tool than simple talking.<br>
Burning bacon or pork chops...makes me impotent..helpless.. vulnerable.. I just fall down and go for the ride.  I stand there with my hat in my hand and watch my best friends become crispy critters...over and over again.  Even in death, they twist and squirm and wave at me while they dehydrate, shrink and turn black.  Don't like eating out.. especially 24 hour breakfast places... wish they would put Taps on the juke box.. serve something that didn't trigger monsters in my head...pound cake and peaches..still a favorite of mine.<br><br>
Ed
